{
  "texts": [
    "Jørgensen et al. [2015] evaluate on a dataset of African-American Vernacular English and show that the then-prevalent POS taggers perform significantly worse.",
    "Darwish et al. [2018] present a CRF-based POS tagger for dialects of Arabic.",
    "The POS tagger is trained on a small set of tweets using features derived from the dialects of interest.",
    "These features are progressive and negation particles.",
    "Eskander et al. [2016] adapt existing morphological analyzers to unseen dialects of Arabic by simulating the low-resource dialects.5.3.2 Deep learning-based approaches."
  ]
}